==English==
===Alternative spellings===
*sometimes hyphenated: '''pan-en-theistically'''
*sometimes either the P or both the P and the initial T are capitalized: '''Panentheistically''', '''PanenTheistically'''
*variations of capitalization and spacing may be combined: '''Pan-en-theistically''', '''Pan-en-Theistically'''
===Etymology===
From {{Gr.}} ''[[πάν]]'' (pán) "all"; [[-en]], and {{Gr.}} ''[[θεός]] (Theós) "god".

===Adjective===
{{en-ad|panentheistically}}
# in a [[panentheistic]] manner

